# Project Overview
This project contains all the code for my Evolutionary Robotics expirements
# Core Architecture
- **Simulation Engine:** We use PyBullet and Taichi for 
physics simulation.
- **Key Directories:**
- `src/classes/`: Contains core object 
definitions (Robot, HillClimber, etc.)
- `src/pybullet/`: Physics simulation 
wrappers.
- `src/taichi/`: High-performance computing 
components.
# Key Terminology
- **Fitness:** The distance a robot travels in 
the simulation.
- **Genotype:** The underlying parameters 
defining the robot (weights, lengths).
- **Phenotype:** The physical manifestation of 
the robot in the simulator.
